{"tid":1925006,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屈福特領隊皮雅臣指摘英首相約翰遜在抗疫上毫無作為","createTime":"2020-03-14T05:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T06:25:34.000Z","uid":117802,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9892b2bd6e31b4dcb43518e8ecba49b238f0f5","tid":1925006,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j5NxkGglYcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj5NxkGglYcw&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCZ6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=1d4dc189\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j5NxkGglYcw</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Watford manager referenced Johnson&rsquo;s press conference on Thursday in saying: &ldquo;<strong>I don&rsquo;t think we had any great leadership last night, listening to the prime minister. I was totally underwhelmed by the lack of leadership and clear message.</strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I heard one of the statements from the prime minister last night talking about listening, and that the decisions would be based on science and that there&rsquo;s no necessarily a greater risk with people being together at sporting venues. If that&rsquo;s based on science, fine, but that doesn&rsquo;t necessarily make sense to me.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<strong>I wouldn&rsquo;t want our fans to be going into a situation where they are fearful of contracting something that could possibly affect either themselves or a member of their family.</strong>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/mar/13/nigel-pearson-condemns-boris-johnson-lack-of-leadership-coronavirus-watford\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffootball%2F2020%2Fmar%2F13%2Fnigel-pearson-condemns-boris-johnson-lack-of-leadership-coronavirus-watford&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCZ6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=25a20413\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/mar/13/nigel-pearson-condemns-boris-johnson-lack-of-leadership-coronavirus-watford</a><br />\n<br />\n中文係 01 link 唔post了<br />\n屈福特領隊皮雅臣（Nigel Pearson）指隊中數名球員出現病徵，其中一人正等候新型冠狀病毒測試結果。賽會公布停賽前，他在記者會上稱要主動應對疫情，「足球業界人人有責，照顧每個人的福祉；我們主動應對，希望英超賽會考慮各方的福祉，作出有力的決策。」，並指摘首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）抗疫不力：「昨晚聽首相發表後，我認為我們沒有偉大的領袖。那記者會的內容所見，欠缺領導才能，毫無清晰訊息，簡直一無所得。」"},{"pid":"5a2e557d81e4f8ceb19762764523899db0f0d3b1","tid":1925006,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"高普<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ES_5uaqWoAERoji?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FES_5uaqWoAERoji%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=8f463ed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n布魯士<br />\nSteve Bruce and his staff at Newcastle are implementing coronavirus contingency plans that have been on the club&rsquo;s tactics board for a month. It is a blueprint that has left every player with a personal training programme to be undertaken in private and the training ground undergoing frequent fumigation procedures during an impending two-week shutdown.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We&rsquo;ve been talking about what would happen if everything was suspended for the past four weeks now,&rdquo; said Newcastle&rsquo;s manager as he endorsed the postponement of all Premier League fixtures until 4 April. <strong>&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t think there&rsquo;s any alternative. My staff and I were sitting watching the TV yesterday and the news [games were then going ahead] came through from the prime minister, and we all thought: &lsquo;OK.&rsquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We were saying:<strong> &lsquo;Well, what happens if one of the players or a manager gets it?&rsquo; And then lo and behold, Mikel Arteta did; it was inevitable, wasn&rsquo;t it?&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Thousands could die from this disease; people&rsquo;s welfare is more important than a football match, a season or a tournament.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/mar/13/steve-bruce-newcastle-prepared-premier-league-fixture-suspension?utm_term=Autofeed&amp;CMP=twt_gu&amp;utm_medium&amp;utm_source=Twitter#Echobox=1584139564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffootball%2F2020%2Fmar%2F13%2Fsteve-bruce-newcastle-prepared-premier-league-fixture-suspension%3Futm_term%3DAutofeed%26CMP%3Dtwt_gu%26utm_medium%26utm_source%3DTwitter%23Echobox%3D1584139564&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCZ6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=3bfe53e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/mar/13/steve-bruce-newcastle-prepared-premier-league-fixture-suspension?utm_term=Autofeed&amp;CMP=twt_gu&amp;utm_medium&amp;utm_source=Twitter#Echobox=1584139564</a>"},{"pid":"f8a3c7c925f6d8f08821c67b761c2805d3fee3bc","tid":1925006,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"定仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615f0a7a0e108a379b8f8d5d8263a1281f260dbc","tid":1925006,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a3c7c925f6d8f08821c67b761c2805d3fee3bc","tid":1925006,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"定仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921e0afb75f3d7b3f4af6caf050ae82f2d47bd7f","tid":1925006,"uid":117802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"Wolves star Diogo Jota has been added to